title: Rebirth of legendary doctor
description: Rebirth of legendary doctor Because of the making a mistake in the capturing soul operation, doctor Xing Aofei was banged by a car and died, but he got a chance to be reborn because of the accident. Unfortunately, once again, Xing Aofei is destined to only be a doctor, and he is also included with the so-called Wrap You Up to the Human’s Pinnacle of Life System’s various pits? The road of Xing Aofei’s rebirth, is destined to be a sad path…… Reborn Doctor 换世医道 The Reborn Super Doctor manhua
